- Both the top and bottom mat of deck reinforcing shall be epoxy-coated or equivalent corrosion protection system as specified in Section 5.1.2.
- Girder stirrups and horizontal shear reinforcement do not require epoxy-coating or equivalent corrosion protection system unless otherwise specified.[[SRC_6]]

