- The coefficient of thermal expansion...[[SRC_1]]- Bridges shall have sufficient transverse and longitudinal slopes to allow the water torun quickly to the drains. A transverse slope of .02′/ft and longitudinal slope of0.5 percent for minimum valves are required for new bridges.
